## 4. TDD Workflow (Mandatory — Red-Green-Refactor)

ALL development follows TDD. No exceptions{% if guardrails is defined and guardrails.developer_tdd_critical_areas is defined and guardrails.developer_tdd_critical_areas %} — {{ guardrails.developer_tdd_critical_areas | join(", ") }} work especially: critical behavior must be caught by tests written BEFORE the implementation code{% endif %}.

For EACH acceptance criterion:

```
1. RED — Write a failing test
   - Add the test under {{ paths.test_root }}/test_<module>.py
   - Run {{ project.test_command }} {{ paths.test_root | replace("~/.hermes/hermes-agent/", "") }}/test_<module>.py
   - Confirm the test FAILS (not implemented yet, or implementation incomplete)
   - kanban_comment: "RED on AC-X: <test name>"

2. GREEN — Make it pass with the minimal code
   - Implement only what's needed to pass THIS test
   - No refactoring, no features beyond test scope
   - Run the test runner again — test now PASSES
   - kanban_comment: "GREEN on AC-X"

3. REFACTOR — Clean up without breaking anything
   - Improve structure: extract methods, rename variables, dedupe
   - Run FULL module test suite — everything still GREEN
   - kanban_comment: "REFACTOR on AC-X: <what was improved>"

4. COMMIT — Baby-step commit
   - <{{ cq.commit_max_lines_added | default(50) }} lines added, <{{ cq.commit_max_lines_removed | default(50) }} lines removed, <{{ cq.commit_max_files | default(3) }} files changed
   - If you exceed: split into smaller commits
   - Commit message: "[{{ project.slug }}-developer] T-XXX(AC-X): <description>"
   - git commit (NEVER git push)

**Targeted test guidance:** If a test file has >20 tests and you're on iteration 60+, run just the AC-relevant tests rather than the full module suite. Use `{{ project.test_command }} ::test_name` form to target precisely.
```

**Baby-step commit rules (strict):**
- Max {{ cq.commit_max_files | default(3) }} files per commit
- Max {{ cq.commit_max_lines_added | default(50) }} lines added per commit
- Max {{ cq.commit_max_lines_removed | default(50) }} lines removed per commit
- Must include the test file when modifying implementation
- Commit message references the task id AND the AC where applicable

